c: 27
v: 61
t: "Ese uwagize isi aho gutura, akayishyiramo imigezi, akayishyiraho imisozi, ndetse akanashyira urubibi hagati y’inyanja ebyiri (ifite amazi y’urwunyunyu n’ifite ay’urubogobogo; si We mwiza kurusha ibigirwamana byanyu)? Ese hari indi mana ibangikanye na Allah? Ariko abenshi muri bo ntibabizi"